{
  "texts": [
    "To address these critical gaps, this study aims to provide a comprehensive review of AI applications at the intersection of personalized nutrition and intelligent food manufacturing.",
    "By synthesizing current research and highlighting both opportunities and constraints, the paper contributes to advancing knowledge and practice in this evolving domain.",
    "Specifically, the study focuses on:",
    "• Personalized dietary planning: exploring AI-driven methods for real-time, individualized nutrition strategies to support chronic disease management and preventive care.",
    "• Food manufacturing innovation: investigating AI applications in food processing, including nutrient preservation, quality control, waste reduction, and resource optimization."
  ]
}